# Glass Design Tokens
#
# Glassmorphism design tokens for macOS-inspired translucent UI.
# Uses backdrop-filter blur, semi-transparent surfaces, and subtle borders.
# No proprietary assets — pure CSS glassmorphism technique.
# Extends the existing theme system via composition.

# Numeric equivalents (u64 hex values for baremetal rendering):
#   see glass_numeric_tokens.spl

use common.ui.design_tokens.{IOSTypographyScale, IOSRadiusTokens, IOSShadowTokens, IOSSpacingScale, IOSAnimationTokens, IOSOpacityTokens}

# =========================================================================
# Glass Color Tokens
# =========================================================================

